{"tid":1662500,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警務處處長XOX下個月就退休喇，接任人將會由副處長DLOM出任","createTime":"2019-10-18T19:50:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-19T02:35:49.000Z","uid":230104,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"90da86a3d30afdc659aebdded3fd61db707e90da","tid":1662500,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T19:50:42.000Z","msg":"由行政長官SB任命<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UZhUjZQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUZhUjZQ.png&h=27dc8ff8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0305fefa923b517e4d778055e6c8eca7dae951ef","tid":1662500,"uid":230104,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T19:54:08.000Z","msg":"佢地唔需要名"},{"pid":"ac035dc56975309bd4b71548949f8d6d18746e27","tid":1662500,"uid":268123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T20:48:52.000Z","msg":"【香城施政報告2019】群策群力 轉危為機<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1656908\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1656908</a><br />\n<br />\n<em><strong>政治問題</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n- 重塑公民身分戶口政策保障國家、香港安全和利益<br />\n- 取消18區區議會、建立地域市政議會<br />\n- 禁止公務人員在任前、任內和任後獲港外榮典<br />\n- 改善高鐵一地兩檢操作方式<br />\n<br />\n<em><strong>便民基建</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n- 興建東鐵、西鐵快速線並完善輕鐵和西鐵聯乘關係<br />\n- 完善機場集體運輸並加強機場、港珠澳大橋協同發展<br />\n- 修正港鐵、巴士可加可減機制<br />\n<br />\n[i]<strong>醫療、教育方向</strong>[i]<br />\n<br />\n- 興建至少四所新區域全科醫院<br />\n- 以減少送院為目標的社區護理服務<br />\n- 重塑教育, 著重知識、技能層次分工<br />\n<br />\n求正評及幫推！"},{"pid":"28fa67f5ccd4405fc6504c7b56cccf41beed6404","tid":1662500,"uid":230104,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T02:32:01.000Z","msg":"以後唔需要俾名佢地"},{"pid":"0b29b4bbd11fb953a4360185554a7a1b290c1f8f","tid":1662500,"uid":65952,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T02:33:42.000Z","msg":"以後唔用警員編號 用警員代號<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ffeb2599f90d2d4fcb7ce0c3a84e97a2b7e2f69","tid":1662500,"uid":91386,"